1-create a node app

npm init --y

2-start the next project

-npm i next react react-dom

3-Go into the package.json

-create three scripts

"dev": "next"
"build": "next build"
"start": "next start"

4-create the pages folder
-inside it create a index.js

in that file create a class based component


import React, { Component } from "react";

class Home extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <h1>Welcome to my page</h1>
      </>
    );
  }
}

export default Home;

--TEST IT--

npm run dev




